data.description: $5,000 Seller Credit with acceptable offer! Experience the tranquility of rural living, all while being just a 15-minute drive from downtown Statesville or Troutman, where you can indulge in shopping, dining, and more. This home, situated on nearly 3/4 acre without any HOA, provides privacy as it sits back from the road. Cozy up to the wood-burning fireplace in the den, or savor your morning coffee in the sunny breakfast area with scenic views of the pasture at the rear of the home. The HVAC system is only a year old, and the metal roof is approximately 10 years old. Appliances such as the refrigerator, washer, and dryer are included. Additionally, it's a short 5.5-mile drive to Lake Norman State Park, offering hiking and biking trails, boat rentals, and other recreational activities.
